  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        outpatients will undergo CGM at two different hemodialysis methods in a croos-over design.
        At the end of the study, it will evaluate inflammation markers intra-and inter-groups
        during the different hemodialysis methods.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with or without diabetes mellitus

          -  ESRD

          -  undergone hemodialysis

